{"tid":878993,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"加息「滿月」：14指標屋苑跌價　德福、新港城最傷","createTime":"2018-10-27T14:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T04:35:02.000Z","uid":83582,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"955a99687f9e76a7618cd9e1585ae4fecd732709","tid":878993,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"10月27日(六) 22:07<br />\n<br />\n加息「滿月」：14指標屋苑跌價　德福、新港城最傷<br />\n<br />\n香港12年來首度加息，至今剛「滿月」。期間樓市明顯轉差，綜合地產代理數據，全港起碼有14個大型指標屋苑在加息後平均樓價報跌，當中有6個屋苑的跌幅更達雙位數。<br />\n<br />\n指標屋苑實用呎價回落，其中，九龍灣德福花園繼早前成交價已跌至「5字頭」。香港置業譚征稱，該屋苑現時平均實用呎價12,866元，較加息前驟跌逾17%。同區的上車熱門屋苑得寶花園實用呎價15,583元，亦急跌超過12%。<br />\n<br />\n長沙灣泓景臺呎價期內呎價下跌達15%。近月不乏劈價成交，中原許永生表示，早前就有一個3座652方呎低層三房戶，叫價在加息後急降19%至1,050萬元售出，呎價僅16,104元，創今年同類單位新低。另藍田港鐵上蓋滙景花園，呎價一個月亦回落5%。<br />\n<br />\n新界區方面，以細價上車屋苑跌勢較急，屯門市廣場期內跌近12%，實用呎價由接近1.5萬元回落至1.31萬元。沙田中心呎價一個月跌10.5%；大圍金獅花園則回落至每方呎15,300元，跌4.4%；而大埔中心亦跌4.6%。馬鞍山新港城一個月內呎價更大幅回落近17%。<br />\n<br />\n至於向來樓價較穩的港島區，則以鴨脷洲海怡半島降價幅度最大。該屋苑在加息後至今，平均呎價跌至1.64萬元，降幅達5.2%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181027/photo/bkn-20181027220735472-1027_00842_001_02b.jpg?20181027221616\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181027%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181027220735472-1027_00842_001_02b.jpg%3F20181027221616&h=f98950ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181027/bkn-20181027220735472-1027_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181027%2Fbkn-20181027220735472-1027_00842_001.html&d=vBTfQxO9OeUepJqlu6n2%2F2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b1eae690\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181027/bkn-20181027220735472-1027_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e62a8a58e48957919a36d4578057a8fcf2c4ff7c","tid":878993,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"樓爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae513d011a7f0c8283410fe725dc6cb1ad27cea","tid":878993,"uid":187956,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"然後再爆升一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4ddcf9c38994d34b22579686bc95b71595f409","tid":878993,"uid":162526,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"自住怕西咩，假跌，肛需，加租，就算下跌您都買唔起啦，下年升到3萬尺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17512e173b7f0478cbcfc5e89f85f9e96718c3d","tid":878993,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acd71adb2d44273f4f27cb5c28d33afba3346454","tid":878993,"uid":162526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17512e173b7f0478cbcfc5e89f85f9e96718c3d","tid":878993,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"加租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73df86c17920e3079854dec109441954d2d64425","tid":878993,"uid":137725,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"本人已去信財金台adman嚴禁會員post過多樓價負面新聞。<br />\n<br />\n大家不要已身試法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ba8cc9beb3745c54c1b0d8e2197731b9bf4c9a","tid":878993,"uid":162526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73df86c17920e3079854dec109441954d2d64425","tid":878993,"uid":137725,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"本人已去信財金台adman嚴禁會員post過多樓價負面新聞。<br />\n<br />\n大家不要已身試法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:10:00.000Z","msg":"post汪總<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as